-- Volkswagen group cars reliability + build quality scores
-- 7 cars: VW Golf GTI(12), VW Phaeton(62), VW Arteon(96), Audi e-tron GT(125), VW Touareg 7L(132), VW Touareg 7P(133), VW Touareg CR(134)
-- Aggregates verified manually using weighted formulas
-- Reliability: eng*0.25 + trn*0.25 + chs*0.15 + elc*0.15 + ease*0.20, catastrophe penalty if any dim < 50
